The '''''Yammka''''' was a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[miid ro'ik]] that served as the [[Flagship/Legends|flagship]] of [[Nas Choka]].

The vessel was young enough to have been christened by [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[Malik Carr]]. It was used by Nas Choka as [[Supreme Commander (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Supreme Commander]] in the campaign against the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]], and remained his [[Command ship/Legends|command ship]] after he became [[Warmaster]], during [[Second Battle of Bilbringi|Operation Trinity]].

==Behind the scenes==
During the [[Defense of Mon Calamari (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Defense of Mon Calamari]] and [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar]], just a few months later, the Warmaster was using a ship named ''[[Yammka's Mount]]''. However, as he still referred to this vessel as the ''Yammka'', it is possible that his original flagship had simply been enlarged and upgraded to become a [[Kor Chokk]].

